original_client_text.markup_text:
If you’re looking for a fancy place for a date, look no further than @shadowbrook_restaurant in Capitola 😉

These guys seriously have it dialed up to 11!

Did you know you can order a free private pick up in one of their old-timey 1940’s style cabs?

Like I said, dialed up to 11!!!

You can take a super cute cable car down to the main entrance, or walk through a beautiful lush garden 😊

💁🏽‍♂️ The wait staff is 👌🏻👌🏻👌🏻

🥩 And the food is even more 👌🏻👌🏻👌🏻👌🏻👌🏻👌🏻

Featured in this video is the blackened prime rib and salmon cakes.

This place isn’t a cheap date! But it is well worth the price of admission.

Let me put it this way, they’ve got a dress code you have to follow, or you’ll have to sit outside 🫣

You are encouraged to dress to impress!

I’d love to know! Have you been to Shadowbrook? What did you think? If not, do you plan on going in the future?
